warren-bank (archive)

This is an F-Droid repository of apps written by Warren Bank. It archives apps that are either forks, demos, experimental or outdated. All source code is GPL-2.0 and available on github: https://github.com/warren-bank?tab=repositories. All APK files are served by 301 redirect to a release asset within the corresponding github repository, and signed by its author with a key having the fingerprint: (SHA-1) 48b2fd2988b9358251b193e5eecac2e43298ef2d, (SHA-256) 7c2a9c3e54cff3cbe6f9f7293aeec465403b2350e03ff85cd0dd32a23d001cee.

Currently it serves 15 apps. To add it to your F-Droid client, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this URL:

https://warren-bank.github.io/fdroid/archive

If you would like to manually verify the fingerprint (SHA-256) of the repository signing key, here it is:
